First Department,

April, 1976

(April 1, 1976) The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v Roberto Rojas, Appellant.

Judgment Supreme Court, New York County, rendered on January 17, 1975, unanimously affirmed. Concur—Markewich, J. P., Lupiano, Birns and Capozzoli, JJ.; Murphy, J. concurs on constraint of People v Esteves (51 AD2d 900). No opinion.
